E '''[[pandemia]] di [[coronavirus]] na 2019–2020''' ta e surgimentu mundial di e malesa di coronavirus tipo [[COVID-19]], kousá pa e sindroma respiratorio severo agudo coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2). E [[vírus]] a wordu raportá pa prome bes na [[Wuhan]], [[provinsia]] [[Hubei]], [[China]], dia 17 di november 2019 <ref>[https://www.scmp.com/news/china/society/article/3074991/coronavirus-chinas-first-confirmed-covid-19-case-traced-back  Coronavirus: China's first confirmed Covid-19 case traced back to 17 November], South China Morning Post, 13 mart 2020</ref> i desde 11 di mart 2020 [[Organisashon Mundial di Salú]] (WHO) a deklará e surgimentu un pandemia.<ref>[https://www.who.int/dg/speeches/detail/who-director-general-s-opening-remarks-at-the-media-briefing-on-covid-19---11-March-2020  WHO Director-General's opening remarks at the media briefing on COVID-19], World Health Organization, 11 mart 2020</ref> 

Te ku 22 di mei 2020 a raportá alrededor di 5.16 mion kaso di COVID-19 na mas ku 188 pais i teritorio, ku a resulta den mas ku 335.000 morto. Mas ku 1.98 mion persona a rekuperá di e virus.<ref>[https://gisanddata.maps.arcgis.com/apps/opsdashboard/index.html#/bda7594740fd40299423467b48e9ecf6 COVID-19 Dashboard di Center for Systems Science and Engineering (CSSE) na John Hopkins University (HU)]</ref> 

