Den forma similar na [[grip]] e vírus ta plama entre persona mediante gotanan respiratorio chiki prosedente di tosamentu.<ref>[https://www.who.int/docs/default-source/coronaviruse/getting-workplace-ready-for-covid-19.pdf  Getting your workplace ready for COVID-19] World Health Organization, 27 febrüari 2020</ref> Entre e momento di ta eksponí i inisio di síntoma tin tipikamente un lapso di sinku dia, pero ku por osila entre dos pa dieskuater dia.<ref name="CDC2020Over222">[https://www.cdc.gov/coronavirus/2019-ncov/about/symptoms.html  Symptoms of Novel Coronavirus (2019-nCoV)], U.S. Centers for Disease Control and Prevention, 10 febrüari 2020</ref><ref>[http://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S0896841120300469 The epidemiology and pathogenesis of coronavirus disease (COVID-19) outbreak], Rothan HA, Byrareddy SN, Journal of Autoimmunity, febrüari 2020</ref> Sintomanan mas komun ta keintura, tosamentu, rosea kortiko.<ref name="CDC2020Over222"/> Komplikashonnan por inklui pulmonia i e sindroma respiratorio agudo. Aktualmente no ta existi bacuna o tratamento spesifiko antiviral, pero investigashon ta andando. Esfuerzonan ta worde dirigi riba maneho di e sintomanan i terapia di sosten. Ta rekomenda medida preventivo manera laba man, mantene [[Distanshamentu sosial|distansia di otro hende]] (en espesial esun ku ta malu), monitoria i auto-isola pa dos siman personanan kual posibelmente ta infekta.<ref name="WHO2020QA">[https://www.who.int/news-room/q-a-detail/q-a-coronaviruses  Q&A on coronaviruses] World Health Organization, 11 febrüari 2020</ref><ref>[https://www.cdc.gov/coronavirus/2019-ncov/specific-groups/high-risk-complications.html Coronavirus Disease 2019 (COVID-19), Centers for Disease Control and Prevention, 11 febrüari 2020</ref>

